[Khyber is a tribal area in the Federally Administered Tribal Area of Pakistan. It is one of the 8 tribal areas, better known as agencies in Pakistan. It ranges from the Tirah valley down to Peshawar. It borders Nangarhar Province to the west, Orakzai Agency to the south, Kurram Agency to the southwest and Peshawar to the east. A map of the Khyber Agency can be accessed at: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Khyber_Agency. - Mod.CP

